      "span_text": "As [CITATION_1] elaborates, productive entrepreneurship is more likely to expand in a marketsupportive institutional framework that is characterised by secure property rights, a fair and balanced judicial system, effective contract enforcement, appropriate business regulation and effective control of government power."
